   166→${data.unfairAdvantage ? `**Unfair Advantage:** ${data.unfairAdvantage}` : ''}
   167→${data.problemValidation ? `**Problem Validation:** ${data.problemValidation}` : ''}
   168→
   169→What is the single most important feature to build first? Leverage the unfair advantage if possible. Be specific and actionable.`;
   170→
   171→    case 'lovable-prompt': {
   172→      // Check if this is automation track with AI analysis
