   198→**Startup Name:** ${data.name}
   199→**Problem:** ${data.problem}
   200→**Solution:** ${data.solution}
   201→**Target Customer:** ${data.customer}
   202→${data.mvpScope ? `**MVP Scope:** ${data.mvpScope}` : ''}
   203→${data.unfairAdvantage ? `**Unfair Advantage:** ${data.unfairAdvantage}` : ''}
   204→${data.successMetrics ? `**Success Metrics:** ${data.successMetrics}` : ''}
   205→
   206→Generate a complete prompt that includes:
